o join seven earlier model <PERSON> Navstars </PERSON> already on patrol. The <ORGANIZATION> Air </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Force </ORGANIZATION> goal is a constellation of 21 of the upgraded payloads in orbit by 1992 to provide total global coverage.
